'''Satish Kalsekar''', ({{lang-mr|सतीश काळसेकर}}) is a Marathi-language poet and writer. He was awarded with [[Sahitya Akademi Award]] in 2013 for his essay collection ''Vachanaryachi Rojanishee''.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://sahitya-akademi.gov.in/sahitya-akademi/pdf/award2013-e.pdf|title=Press Release |publisher=Sahitya Akademi |date=18 December 2013|accessdate=27 February 2018}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last1=Tankha|first1=Madhur|title=Sahitya Akademi awards presented|url=http://www.thehindu.com/books/books-authors/sahitya-akademi-awards-presented/article5774348.ece|accessdate=27 February 2018|date=11 March 2014}}</ref> He is predominantly known for his work as poet. His popular collections of poems are Indriyopnishad (इंद्रियोपनिषद), Sakshat (साक्षात) and Vilambit (विलंबित).<ref name="mata">{{cite news|title=सतीश काळसेकर|url=https://maharashtratimes.indiatimes.com/editorial/manasa/satish-kalsekar/articleshow/27697299.cms|accessdate=27 February 2018|publisher=maharashtratimes|date=21 December 2013|language=mr}}</ref>
